Problem :
        * View messages
        * Easy DoS

Description:
------------

View messages:
==============

File with all chat sessions are in txt file (msg.txt) and everybody can 
read it

Easy DoS:
=========

If the size msg.txt will be more than 326 kb a window of a chat will 
start to be reloaded on some times per one second, then fastly, fastly 
while eventually and at all it will cease to be reloaded

Exploits:
---------

http://[somehost]/vchat/msg.txt
http://[somehost]/vchat/chat.php  << In message field u must paste 326 kb 
of text

